Sub-Alias

This module provides easy function aliasing, it lets you say:

    alias foo => 'bar';

Instead of

    sub foo; *foo = \&bar;

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install



DEPENDENCIES

B::Hooks::Parser, Sub::Exporter

